README.md
     5→## Usage
     7→To start using the library, install it in your project:
     8→
     9→```bash
    10→npm install sonner
    11→```
    12→
    13→Add `<Toaster />` to your app, it will be the place where all your toasts will be rendered.
    14→After that you can use `toast()` from anywhere in your app.
    15→
    16→```jsx
    17→import { Toaster, toast } from 'sonner';
    18→
    19→// ...
    20→
    21→function App() {
    22→  return (
    23→    <div>
    24→      <Toaster />
    25→      <button onClick={() => toast('My first toast')}>Give me a toast</button>
    26→    </div>
    27→  );
    28→}
    29→```
    30→
    31→## Documentation
    33→Find the full API reference in the [documentation](https://sonner.emilkowal.ski/getting-started).
